public Form.LayoutParams(int width,
                         int height,
                         float weight)




Creates a new set of layout parameters with the specified width, height
 and weight.





Parameters:
width - the width, either #FILL_PARENT,
        #WRAP_CONTENT or a fixed size in pixels
height - the height, either #FILL_PARENT,
        #WRAP_CONTENT or a fixed size in pixels
weight - the weight
